room_title: Escape room "The Billionaire's Den" by Escape Room Mystery in King of Prussia
review: Had a great time trying to escape from the Billionaires den! Had a great guide (Dan)! Highly recommend coming here with your family!

room_title: Escape room "The Billionaire's Den" by Escape Room Mystery in King of Prussia
review: Our family had a mini reunion with 8 family members. 6 of the 8 people had never attempted any escape rooms......We had a blast and made it with seconds to go. Dan, our support guy was great and only stepped in when we were only half bright!!!! Thank you for a great time and we ALL loved it. We will be doing more soon.

room_title: Escape room "The Billionaire's Den" by Escape Room Mystery in King of Prussia
review: I had the best time ever in the Billionaire's Den! It was down to the final seconds... Tougher than I expected, but it just added to the challenge. Until next time!
